    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1052971298">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1052971298" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1052971298" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1052971298">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sarcophagus/">Sarcophagus</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-06-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">无愧剑桥民国史和共和国史多章撰稿，视野开阔，布局精致，比对各社会阶层在抗战结束初期与后期对国共态度转换，回答内战何以速决。史料纵受时代局限，亦能点面结合，尤重地区差异。不仅擅长的学界写得精彩，土改部分占全书近1/4，繁而不乱。真正回到历史现场、体味人心选择之势</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="816897791">
