  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3305056">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3305056/" class="title-link">动物庄园</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3305056"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lovedzc/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1000999-69.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lovedzc/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">丁丁虫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-01"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-01 00:50:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3305056_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读到“重返城市”那一章的时候，看到书中举出种种数字证实工人在解放初期自觉加班，不禁想起奥威尔的《动物庄园》里那匹对革命忠实无比的马。  那时候的知识分子虽然已经知道未来的掌权者绝不会是斯诺鲍，但多少还是存着一丝希冀，盼望不会落入拿破仑的魔掌吧。  只是知识分子...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3305056/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 7没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中国青年出版社1997版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3305056_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3305056_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










